      "A53-A55  [tr OldIndian]: [trans [list 1.d4 Nf6 2.c4 d6]]" \
      "A57-A59  [tr BenkoGambit]: [trans [list 1.d4 Nf6 2.c4 c5 3.d5 b5]]" \
      "A60-A79  [tr ModernBenoni]: [trans [list 1.d4 Nf6 2.c4 c5 3.d5 e6]]" \
      "A80-A99  [tr DutchDefence]: 1.d4 f5" \
